{"tid":203314,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登時事邏輯總結捐肝事件","createTime":"2017-04-16T07:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-17T13:25:54.000Z","uid":12443,"like":105,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d982caecd456c8c2df6c41e8947fa59a7812c4b","tid":203314,"uid":12443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T07:58:19.000Z","msg":"捐肝者<br />\n收左錢，貪錢<br />\n唔收，扮大愛<br />\n收左但捐出去，通哂天仲自己落袋？<br />\n捐肝，搏出位收左錢你唔知<br />\n唔捐，自私港豬<br />\n做完手術之後有事，自己攞黎衰<br />\n<br />\n總之連登圍內講啲同常理相反既陰謀論就會覺得自己睇得好透，眾人皆醉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有一班仲離譜，上連登上到以為呢度有人咐和自己，自己講既野就係真理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醒下啦<br />\n<br />\n其實捐肝事件都只係例子，套用番落去撞車or其他事都可以，不過有死人既就會有啲唔同，班人要懶係好唔忿氣咁加句&quot;積口德&quot;黎反諷，因為之前比一大班人串過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n將做人基本尊重本末倒置仲要覺得自己好威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我奉勸上開連登既咁多位正常思維人類，做你自己覺得啱既野就可以，網絡其他人既說話，係唔需要理會，除非係有助自己學習同進步成為一個更好既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8758a1cd73e0612c592c7baf72588036789c2f3a","tid":203314,"uid":27256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:00:48.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"89aeda5d95a4673da01c2d392f1732daa3e7572f","tid":203314,"uid":29270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-16T08:01:01.000Z","msg":"之前大學男生求心臟果單野 有批人話<br />\n<br />\n屍體器官捐贈 -&gt; 咒人死，醫生殺人拎器官，叫人去自殺<br />\n<br />\n百思不得其解<br />\n到底係乜野邏輯黎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd149bf27c7804264880b065e6514b0093090b11","tid":203314,"uid":9781